HEADWORD: Tautological
<hw>Tau`to*log"ic*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>tautologique</ets>.]</ety> <def>Involving tautology; having the
same signification; <as>as, <ex>tautological</ex> expression</as>.</def>
-- <wordforms><wf>Tau`to*log"ic*al*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Tautological echo</b></col>, <cd>an echo that repeats the
same sound or syllable many times.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

